com.dummyvendor.model

Class DummyVendorFraudScoreResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dummyvendor.model.DummyVendorFraudScoreResponse

  • public class DummyVendorFraudScoreResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    A greatly simplified representation of a particular vendor's input DTO for a fraud quote request. For a given vendor, this DTO may be a supplied vendor API (jar dependency) rather than a class you need to create.
